Package GUIElements

Class Pane

java.lang.Object
GUIElements.GUIElement
GUIElements.Container
GUIElements.Pane
All Implemented Interfaces:
ScrollBarListener
Direct Known Subclasses:
LeafPane, SplitHTMLDocument
public abstract class Pane
extends Container
Superclass for HTMLDocument and SplitHTMLDocument. It defines the needed methods for the tree hierarchy necessary for the splitting and deleting of panes. Our implementation works on the basis of a tree structure.
